text: Travis Barker has been rushed to the
hospital with wife Kourtney Kardashian
by his side the Blink-182 drummer was
taken by ambulance to Cedar Sinai
Medical Center in Los Angeles on June
28th amid the health scare the
musician's 16 year old daughter Alabama
Barker asked for prayers on her
Instagram story though she did not
provide additional details E news has
reached out to Travis's rep for comment
and has not heard back hours before the
medical emergency Travis sparked concern
among some fans on Twitter with the
cryptic message God saved me however
others interpreted the Tweet to be a
reference to a song by close friend and
collaborator Machine Gun Kelly Travis's
hospitalization comes about a month
after he and Courtney tied the knot in
Portofino Italy with their family and
friends in attendance though it's been a
rocky few weeks for the couple with
Courtney recently making a full recovery
from her second covid-19 diagnosis we
are wishing Travis a speedy recovery
[Music]
thank you
